EXEC IDEAS
==========

delphi program that reads processed loggie logs and draws a live relationship chart and stats

~admin ignore on|off # completely ignores a channel (including logging)

~karma on|off

SN crawler/mapper

~remind
set bucket with start time
if exec restarts, check all remind buckets to see if any haven't expired yet
and reset them with new sleep time to trigger at correct intended time

freepascal-ize SN log parsing and searching